52:33.160 --> 52:35.527
<i>♪ She's pure as New York snow</i>

52:37.120 --> 52:39.646
<i>♪ She got Bette Davis eyes</i>

52:42.760 --> 52:45.923
<i>♪ And she'll tease you
She'll unease you</i>

52:46.720 --> 52:50.361
<i>♪ All the better
just to please you</i>

52:50.840 --> 52:52.683
<i>♪ She's precocious</i>

52:52.760 --> 52:54.683
<i>♪ And she knows just</i>

52:54.760 --> 52:58.890
<i>♪ What it takes
to make a pro blush ♪</i>

